## Custom Domains

Without a custom domain, auth emails show `projectref.supabase.co` in links — not your brand.

```
Dashboard → Settings → Custom Domains → Add custom domain
  1. Enter your domain: api.yourdomain.com
  2. Add the required CNAME record to your DNS (shown in dashboard)
  3. Wait for DNS propagation (up to 24 hours)
  4. Supabase provisions SSL certificate automatically

What changes:
  API URL: https://api.yourdomain.com (instead of https://ref.supabase.co)
  Auth emails: links show api.yourdomain.com
  Update: NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL in all environments
```

Note: Custom domains are available on Pro plan and above.
